hesize Pandas data frame\nmanipulating programs in Python using simple abstractions like types and column\nlabels of a data frame. Absynthe reaches parity with AutoPandas, a deep\nlearning based tool for the same benchmark suite. In summary, our results\ndemonstrate Absynthe is a promising step forward towards a general-purpose\napproach to synthesis that may broaden the applicability of synthesis to more\n$\\ldots$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Feb 2023 19:27:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 21:09:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
